          <p><a href="#">Terry Ednacot</a>: Program manager</p>
          <p><a href="#">Rachel Andrews</a>: Content lead</p>
          <p><a href="#">Surma</a>: Container query polyfiller</p>
          <p><a href="#">Emma Twersky</a>: Site contributor</p>
          <p><a href="#">Kevin Lozandier</a>: Site contributor</p>
          <p><a href="#">Cole Murphy</a>: Site contributor</p>
        </div>
        <p class="callout">Check out <a href="https://web.dev">web.dev</a> for more web development content, all year long.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</footer>